, ♀. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[667,688,1964,1990]" pageId="45" pageNumber="46">A</emphasis>
. Lateral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[867,887,1965,1991]" pageId="45" pageNumber="46">B</emphasis>
. Head (SEM). 
